summary:
Eyes are the window to the soul. Vanilla eyes are a window to a low graphical nightmare.
Doesn´t your character deserve soul-piercing eyes?
descriptionHtml:
[center][img width=744,height=265]https://78.media.tumblr.com/9e988d11fc96ae3eb40a444fa79f460b/tumblr_pbg4tywF2g1wb3iqho1_1280.png[/img]﻿[/center][center] 
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/18430/][color=#fff2cc][u][b][size=4]Now for Skyrim SE , DOWNLOAD IT HERE[/size][/b][/u][/color][/url]﻿

Eyes will forever be something we humans find interesting in a non-creepy away.
And Skyrim's Eyes are terrible, in every way. So I upgraded them to look even more smashing.
And to look good with or without fancy enbs.  

 Ok, some fun facts about eyes:
1.You blink about 12 times every minute.
2. The average blink lasts for about 1/10th of a second.
3. Seeing is such a big part of everyday life that it requires about half of the brain to get involved.

Take a cookie on the table and have a nice day.
